data.description: Step into luxury w/ this captivating one-level home nestled on almost half an acre, boasting a prime location near freeways & delightful restaurants. Revel in the comfort of 3bdrms & 2 newly renovated bathrooms in the main house, featuring HW floors in the living & dining areas, complemented by plush newer carpeting in the bdrms. A separate ADU complete w/ a walk-in shower, bdrm, living & kitchenette – perfect for out-of-town guests. The backyard beckons w/ two storage buildings, an open-air gazebo, & a tranquil pond. Discover the new features of this residence, w/ Milgard Windows, Insulation, Smart 50G WH, & a heat pump for the seperate living.  New electrical panel & solar panels, ensuring this home is as efficient as it is inviting.
